  "detailed_description": "<strong>Exorcist Simulator is a co‑op horror game.</strong><br>Break into haunted places, grab cursed relics, and send the demon back to hell — or let one player become that demon and hunt the team.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487140/extras/8118d45a57cb449b9961e4587bc8eb2e.poster.avif?t=1750255329\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487140/extras/8118d45a57cb449b9961e4587bc8eb2e.webm?t=1750255329\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487140/extras/8118d45a57cb449b9961e4587bc8eb2e.mp4?t=1750255329\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Play as part of a team of exorcists using sacred relics, holy rituals, and magical spells to survive and exorcise the demonic threat. Or embrace the darkness and become the Devil himself, hunting down the intruders one by one. Every match is a tense, atmospheric battle of wits, will, and survival.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Choose Your Role:</h2><strong>Exorcists:</strong> Work together to locate cursed artifacts, solve arcane puzzles, and banish the Devil before time runs out.<br><strong>The Devil:</strong> Possess, deceive, and destroy — your goal is simple: eliminate the exorcists before they cleanse the grounds.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487140/extras/98ead2292324a5e33fdca987c0ff62c7.poster.avif?t=1750255329\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487140/extras/98ead2292324a5e33fdca987c0ff62c7.webm?t=1750255329\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487140/extras/98ead2292324a5e33fdca987c0ff62c7.mp4?t=1750255329\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🧩 Key Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Work together:</strong> search every room, solve quick puzzles, finish the banishing ritual.<br></li><li><strong>Become the Devil:</strong> possess objects, stalk the living, strike when they panic.<br></li><li><strong>Face fresh scares</strong>: two hand‑built maps, random relic spots, new tricks every match.<br></li><li><strong> 4 Unique Characters:</strong> Each with their own strengths, skills, and ways to face the supernatural.</li></ul><br><br>Are you ready to cast out evil... or drag your enemies into it?",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Exorcist Simulator is a co‑op horror game.</strong><br>Break into haunted places, grab cursed relics, and send the demon back to hell — or let one player become that demon and hunt the team.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487140/extras/8118d45a57cb449b9961e4587bc8eb2e.poster.avif?t=1750255329\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487140/extras/8118d45a57cb449b9961e4587bc8eb2e.webm?t=1750255329\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487140/extras/8118d45a57cb449b9961e4587bc8eb2e.mp4?t=1750255329\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Play as part of a team of exorcists using sacred relics, holy rituals, and magical spells to survive and exorcise the demonic threat. Or embrace the darkness and become the Devil himself, hunting down the intruders one by one. Every match is a tense, atmospheric battle of wits, will, and survival.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Choose Your Role:</h2><strong>Exorcists:</strong> Work together to locate cursed artifacts, solve arcane puzzles, and banish the Devil before time runs out.<br><strong>The Devil:</strong> Possess, deceive, and destroy — your goal is simple: eliminate the exorcists before they cleanse the grounds.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487140/extras/98ead2292324a5e33fdca987c0ff62c7.poster.avif?t=1750255329\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487140/extras/98ead2292324a5e33fdca987c0ff62c7.webm?t=1750255329\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487140/extras/98ead2292324a5e33fdca987c0ff62c7.mp4?t=1750255329\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🧩 Key Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Work together:</strong> search every room, solve quick puzzles, finish the banishing ritual.<br></li><li><strong>Become the Devil:</strong> possess objects, stalk the living, strike when they panic.<br></li><li><strong>Face fresh scares</strong>: two hand‑built maps, random relic spots, new tricks every match.<br></li><li><strong> 4 Unique Characters:</strong> Each with their own strengths, skills, and ways to face the supernatural.</li></ul><br><br>Are you ready to cast out evil... or drag your enemies into it?",
